# Non-functional requirements

## Purpose

Record quality attributes: performance, security, reliability, operability, accessibility, and compliance. These inform SPEC sections on data, state, and platform.

## Categories

| Category | Summary |
|----------|---------|
| Performance | Latency, throughput, concurrency |
| Security | AuthN/Z, data protection, auditing |
| Reliability | Availability, DR, idempotency |
| Operability | Logging, metrics, runbooks |

## Requirements

### `REQ-NFR-001` Performance (draft)

Document latency targets, throughput, and scalability expectations (load growth, peak factors).

### `REQ-NFR-002` Security (draft)

Threat model highlights, encryption, secrets handling, and audit expectations.

